asement + Stilt+ 21 stories+1 Amenities + 3 Duplex; of total heights 99.7m. We have performed reviews on structural design basis report and; analysis and design peer review of the ETAB, STAAD and safe models of software’s and; compare with manual calculations. Also, we did proof check of detailing of column, beam,; slabs, shear wall, foundation, retaining walls and water tanks.; 4. Steel dome VR Metropolitan, Delhi mall, Khyber Pass, New Delhi: -; The dome design project of diameter 32.227m and 12.175 m height of steel tube members,; steel plate roofing material and concrete admixture with shear compactors. The support is; considered 12 pin and 8 rollers. Dome is modelled by using ETAB Software.; 5. Unitech Grande Sector 96, 97 & 98 Noida, UP: -; The project consists of towers of Amber, Burgundy and Uni-home cluster with amber 7; towers, burgundy- 6 towers and amber 4 towers for modelling and design of tower and; foundation by ETAB and SAFE Software. This project is ongoing for retrofit of all Unitech; tower with IIT Roorkee."}]'::jsonb, 'F:\Resume All 1\Resume PDF\DHARM CV 13.4.pdf', 'Name: Dharm Singh

